'''般尼2010年至2011年球季'''（{{lang-en|'''2010–11 Burnley F.C. season'''}}）是[[伯恩利足球俱乐部|伯恩利足球俱乐部]]在[[英格蘭足球聯賽|英格蘭足球聯賽]]第112個球季，是於[[2009年至2010年英格蘭超級聯賽|上季]]從[[英超|英超]]降班後首個處於第二級聯賽的球季。

==記事==
* 2010年6月3日前鋒[[Steven_Fletcher_(footballer)|-{zh-hans:斯蒂芬·弗莱彻; zh-hk:史提芬·費查;}-]]（Steven Fletcher）以破球會收取轉會費紀錄的約650萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]轉投[[伍尔弗汉普顿流浪足球俱乐部|狼隊]]<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/wolverhampton_wanderers/8719151.stm |title=Burnley striker Steven Fletcher makes Wolves switch |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2010-06-03 |accessdate=2010-06-04 |archive-date=2020-10-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201029084926/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/wolverhampton_wanderers/8719151.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。
* 2010年12月29日雖然球隊位列聯賽榜第7位，距離附加賽席位僅差2分兼少賽1場，領隊[[Brian_Laws|布萊恩·劳斯]]（Brian Laws）仍然於執教不足1年而被革職<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/b/burnley/9326516.stm |title=Boss Brian Laws shown door by Burnley |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2010-12-29 |accessdate=2010-12-30 |archive-date=2020-12-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201229000855/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/b/burnley/9326516.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。
* 2010年12月30日一隊教練[[Stuart_Gray_(footballer_born_1960)|史超活·格雷]]（Stuart Gray）出任看守領隊<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/b/burnley/9328016.stm |title=Burnley make Stuart Gray caretaker boss |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2010-12-30 |accessdate=2010-12-31 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307003608/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/b/burnley/9328016.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。
* 2011件月16日聘請前[[伯恩茅斯足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:伯恩茅斯; zh-hk:般尼茅夫;}-]]主帥[[埃迪·霍維|埃迪·霍維]]接任領隊，簽約三年半，其副手[[Jason_Tindall|杰森·廷德尔]]（Jason Tindall）亦跟隨上任<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/b/burnley/9360426.stm |title=Eddie Howe appointed Burnley manager |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2011-01-16 |accessdate=2011-01-17 |archive-date=2019-10-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191010163557/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/b/burnley/9360426.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。
* 2011年4月16日主場2-1擊敗[[斯旺西城足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:斯旺西; zh-hk:史雲斯;}-]]，[[隊長_(足球)|隊長]][[格拉汉姆·亚历山大|-{zh-hans:格拉汉姆·亚历山大; zh-hk:亞歷山大;}-]]於完場前87分鐘後補上陣<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/13022994.stm |title=Burnley 2-1 Swansea |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2011-04-16 |accessdate=2011-04-19 |archive-date=2011-04-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110423065750/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/13022994.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，是他職業生涯第1,000場上陣<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/blogs/paulfletcher/2011/04/alexander_joins_the_1000_club.html#286904 |title=Alexander the great joins the 1,000 club |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2011-04-17 |accessdate=2011-04-19 |archive-date=2019-09-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190911175458/https://www.bbc.co.uk/blogs/paulfletcher/2011/04/alexander_joins_the_1000_club.html#286904 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。
* 2011年4月30日作客0-1負於競爭對手[[列斯聯足球會|-{zh-hans:利兹联; zh-hk:列斯聯;}-]]後正式告別附加賽席位<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/13174157.stm |title=Leeds 1-0 Burnley |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2011-04-30 |accessdate=2011-05-06 |archive-date=2011-05-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110503160606/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/13174157.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。
* 2011年5月5日就球隊與[[列斯聯足球會|-{zh-hans:利兹联; zh-hk:列斯聯;}-]]日前的8張[[黃牌|黃牌]]賽事期間兩隊球員發生衝突，[[英格蘭足球總會|英格蘭足球總會]]起訴兩會未能屬下球員維持有序及/或容忍挑釁的行為<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/13299686.stm |title=Leeds United and Burnley charged by FA |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2011-05-05 |accessdate=2011-05-06 |archive-date=2011-05-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110510084354/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/13299686.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。
* 2011年5月10日球會因[[列斯聯足球會|-{zh-hans:利兹联; zh-hk:列斯聯;}-]]的衝突事件被判罰5,000[[英鎊|英鎊]]<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/13299686.stm |title=Football Association hits Burnley with £5,000 fine |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2011-05-10 |accessdate=2011-05-11 |archive-date=2011-05-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110510084354/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/13299686.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

